These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-8-1::.
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: daisy, lily
The people use 2 different means of transport: airplane, scooter
1. the person driving the airplane is on the right of the person driving the scooter##1
2. the person who growsdaisy is not to the right of the person driving the scooter##8

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |    2     |
| Flower        | daisy   | lily   |
| Transport   | scooter | airplane |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-8-2::.
The people use 2 different means of transport: subway, airplane
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: cycling, lacrosse
1. the person who's sport is cycling is not to the left of the person driving the airplane##8
2. the person who's sport is cycling is somewhere to the right of the person driving the airplane##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2    |
| Transport   | airplane | subway   |
| Sport      | lacrosse | cycling |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-8-3::.
There 2 different types of food: cabbage, peach
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: documentary, time-travel
1. the person eating cabbage is not to the left of the person watching time-travel movies##8
2. the person eating peach is on the left of the person watching time-travel movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |
| Food          | peach | cabbage |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary   | time-travel     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-8-4::.
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: swisher, tiparillo
2 different pets are kept: dog, fish
1. the owner of the dog is not to the right of the swisher-smoker##8
2. the swisher-smoker is on the right of the owner of the dog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1    |  2   |
| Cigar   | tiparillo | swisher |
| Pet    | dog    | fish |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-8-5::.
